    "parsed_json": null,
    "stderr": "",
    "stdout": "export_changes\n\nFamily\n  Management\n\nDescription\n  Fold every published layer above the base (newest-wins, whiteout/opaque aware) into a compressed delta stream, fetch it from the sandbox daemon, and apply it onto --dest or write it as an archive. Forwards export_layerstack and read_export_chunk requests to the sandbox daemon.\n\nUsage\n  sandbox-manager-cli export_changes --sandbox-id ID --dest PATH [--format dir|tar|tar-zst]\n\nArguments\n  --sandbox-id string required\n    Sandbox id.\n\n  --dest path required\n    Absolute host destination: directory for dir format, archive file for tar formats.\n\n  --format string optional\n    Output format: dir, tar, or tar-zst.\n    Default: dir\n\n\nExamples\n  sandbox-manager-cli export_changes --sandbox-id sbox-1 --dest /home/me/myproject\n  sandbox-manager-cli export_changes --sandbox-id sbox-1 --dest /tmp/delta.tar.zst --format tar-zst\n\nRelated Operations\n  inspect_sandbox\n  checkpoint_squash\n"
  },
